abstract_str: nathan bates and __liaquat__ ali were part of a gang targeting range rovers . duo visited sellers that advertised on __autotrader__ and clone their car keys . they then returned to steal the luxury vehicles in a scam worth # 110,000 . body of fellow gang member michael griffiths ' was found in river __thame__ . ali was jailed for three and half years while bates was jailed for 15 months .
